<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="ie=edge">
    <title>Document</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="./css/basic.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="./css/demo.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="./css/landing_settings_email.css">
</head>

<body>
    <div class="ap_cnep_pagelet">
        <div class="headerText">
            <span> 更改电子邮件 </span>
        </div>
        <div class="ap_cnep_subtitle">请使用下面的表单更改帐户的邮箱地址。请在下次登录或下订单时使用新地址。</div>
        <table id="ap_cnep_table" class="ap_form_table">
            <tbody>
                <tr>
                    <td colspan="2">
                        <div id="ap_cnep_section1_title" class="ap_section_title">
                            <h2>您的新邮箱地址是什么？</h2>
                        </div>
                    </td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <td>
                        <div class="right">
                            <span class="ap_input_label ">当前邮箱地址： </span>
                        </div>
                    </td>
                    <td>
                        <span class="ap_forminput emailAddress">
                            5017140@qq.com
                        </span>
                    </td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <td></td>
                    <td>
                        <div class="form_alert" style="display:none;">请输入您的新电子邮件地址</div>
                    </td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <td></td>
                    <td>
                        <div class="form_alert" style="display:none;">邮箱地址不符</div>
                    </td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <td>
                        <div class="right">
                            <span id="ap_cnep_email_new_label" class="ap_input_label">
                                <label for="ap_email_new">新邮箱地址：</label>
                            </span>
                        </div>
                    </td>
                    <td>
                        <span class="ap_forminput">
                            <input type="email" style="height: 16px" class="newEmailAddress">
                        </span>
                    </td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <td></td>
                    <td>
                        <div class="form_alert" style="display:none;">请再次输入您的新电子邮件</div>
                    </td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <td>
                        <div class="right">
                            <span class="ap_input_label">
                                <label for="ap_email_new_check">请再次输入新邮箱地址：</label>
                            </span>
                        </div>
                    </td>
                    <td>
                        <span class="ap_forminput">
                            <input type="againEmail" style="height: 16px">
                        </span>
                    </td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <td></td>
                    <td>
                        <div class="form_alert" style="display:none;">请输入您的密码：</div>
                    </td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <td>
                        <div class="right">
                            <span class="ap_input_label">
                                <label for="ap_password">密码：‎</label>
                            </span>
                        </div>
                    </td>
                    <td>
                        <span class="ap_forminput">
                            <input name="password" type="password" style="height: 16px" >
                        </span>
                    </td>
                    <td>
                        <span>
                            <div class="ap_caps_warn ap_standard_caps_warn_table" style="visibility:hidden;">
                                <b>大写锁定键已开启。</b>
                                <font color="black">这可能导致
                                    <br>您所输入的密码不正确。</font>
                            </div>

                        </span>
                    </td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <td colspan="2">
                        <div class="ap_section_title">
                            <h2> 请输入图片中的字符 </h2>
                        </div>
                    </td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <td>
                        <div class="right">

                            <div class="ap_input_label">
                                图像:
                                <div id="ap_captcha_refresh" class="right tiny">
                                    <span class="hidden faded" style="display: none;">
                                        看不清, 换一张
                                    </span>
                                    <span>
                                        <a href="javascript:;" style="display: inline;">
                                            看不清, 换一张
                                        </a>

                                    </span>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </td>
                    <td>
                        <div>
                            <img src="">
                        </div>
                    </td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <td></td>
                    <td>
                        <div class="form_alert" style="display:none;">
                            输入以上字符
                        </div>
                    </td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <td>
                        <div class="right">
                            <div class="ap_input_label">
                                请输入图片中的字符
                                <div class="tiny right">
                                    <a href="">需要更多帮助?</a>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </td>
                    <td>
                        <div>
                            <input type="text">
                        </div>
                    </td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <td>&nbsp;</td>
                    <td>
                        <span class="in-amzn-btn btn-prim-med" id="cnep_1D_submit_button" unselectable="on">
                            <span>
                                <input type="submit" value="保存更改" tabindex="4" class="submitBtn">
                            </span>
                        </span>
                    </td>
                </tr>
            </tbody>
        </table>
    </div>
</body>
<script src="./js/jquery-3.3.1.min.js " type="text/javascript"></script>
<script src="./js/webjs/prompt.js" type="text/javascript"></script>
<script src="./js/public.js " type="text/javascript"></script>
<script src="./js/webjs/landing_settings_email.js"></script>

</html>